QuestData.Title: A Time of Revelation
QuestData.Description:
I can feel Ateena's dark voodoo up ahead. We need to stop whatever she is planning with dis "G'huun".
Be ready for anything, $n. We do not know what power Ateena truly has.
I do know one thing. If G'huun is threatening my people, den it will die, just like Ateena.

Objectives.Objective: Speak with Talanji at the overlook
